    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour light dancing across the liquid-smooth curves of this masterpiece. To sit behind the wheel is to step into a bygone era of effortless elegance and raw, unbridled soul. Every stitch in the supple leather tells a story of craftsmanship, while the engine hums with the steady heartbeat of a champion ready for its next grand adventure. This isn't merely a vehicle; it\u2019s a portal to a more glamorous life, preserved in a state that feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor of a dream.",
      "price": 46500.0,
